250Nahetupaccayā naārammaṇapaccayā naadhipatiyā ekaṃ, na anantare ekaṃ, nasamanantare ekaṃ, naaññamaññe ekaṃ, naupanissaye ekaṃ, napurejāte ekaṃ, napacchājāte ekaṃ, naāsevane ekaṃ, nakamme ekaṃ, navipāke ekaṃ, naāhāre ekaṃ, naindriye ekaṃ, najhāne ekaṃ, namagge ekaṃ, nasampayutte ekaṃ, navippayutte ekaṃ, nonatthiyā ekaṃ, novigate ekaṃ…pe… .
